01:01:27,925 --> 01:01:29,961
Don't fuck with me, Ben.
I'm not in the mood.

734
01:01:31,513 --> 01:01:34,056
So, are you in Milwaukee?
- No, I'm in Michigan.

735
01:01:34,921 --> 01:01:38,029
Your guy was spotted in Milwaukee.
- I know that, I saw it on the news.

736
01:01:38,317 --> 01:01:42,341
And here I thought we were the news.
