865
01:11:14,372 --> 01:11:16,000
Yeah, some of you got lucky.

866
01:11:16,773 --> 01:11:18,905
It wasn't luck.
- Well, what was then?

867
01:11:19,481 --> 01:11:22,605
Jed...
what was it?

868
01:11:23,869 --> 01:11:25,685
We didn't kill anybody.

869
01:11:26,865 --> 01:11:30,562
Jed, I need to find Mimi.
