871
01:11:35,866 --> 01:11:39,030
Donal told you... fuck!

872
01:11:39,798 --> 01:11:40,951
Fuck!

873
01:11:41,046 --> 01:11:42,277
Does it matter?

874
01:11:42,663 --> 01:11:44,182
Jed, does it matter?

875
01:11:45,358 --> 01:11:49,579
Look, the truth? I haven't talked to Mimi
since bell-bottoms went out of style, okay?

876
01:11:50,171 --> 01:11:52,808
I mean, how do you know she's even still alive?
- I don't.

877
01:11:53,383 --> 01:11:55,979
